		</p>
      <p> See 
		  <xref href="https://marketing.adobe.com/resources/help/en_US/target/target/r_release_notes.html" format="https" scope="external">Target Release Notes</xref> for the latest
		  information. 
		</p>
      <p>
        <b>
          <keyword>Recommendations</keyword>
        </b>
      </p>
      <p>This release includes the following enhancements: 
		</p>
      <p>
        <table id="table_D0DD38395B6C4CB4BD334A02C7487AA4">
          <tgroup cols="2">
            <colspec colnum="1" colname="col1" colwidth="*" />
            <colspec colnum="2" colname="col2" colwidth="*" />
            <thead>
              <row>
                <entry colname="col1">Enhancement 
				  </entry>
                <entry colname="col2">Description 
				  </entry>
              </row>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <row>
                <entry colname="col1">
                  <!--Recs-2635-->Improved past behavior
					 algorithms 
				  </entry>
                <entry colname="col2">
                  <p>Allow for past behavior algorithms to serve more than just
						the last viewed item. 
					 </p>
                </entry>
              </row>
              <row>
                <entry colname="col1">
                  <!--Recs-2730-->Improved exclusion rules 
				  </entry>
                <entry colname="col2">
                  <p>Exclusion rules are now applied to recently viewed items. 
					 </p>
                </entry>
              </row>
            </tbody>
          </tgroup>
        </table>
      </p>
      <p>This release includes the following fix: 
		</p>
      <p>
        <ul id="ul_8BF6486FE7724C7BB2A25114C54F3CBE">
          <li id="li_206B11A5515A44B3BDE1942021EDCFF4">
            <!--Recs-2562-->Fixed an
			 issue that prevented navigating directly to product search result pages having
			 more than 3 digits. 
		  </li>
